tion may play a role. However, it is clear the\nrelationship between rotation and activity is more complex than a steady\ndecrease over time.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Feb 2022 17:23:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-02"}
