 our knowledge, this paper is the first work\nto comprehensively and systematically summarize the recent advances of\nTransformers for modeling time series data. We hope this survey will ignite\nfurther research interests in time series Transformers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Feb 2022 01:43:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 2 Mar 2022 00:58:08 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 7 Mar 2022 05:52:13 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 10 Feb 2023 21:00:08 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Thu, 11 May 2023 21:47:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-15"}
