s, and are\ndynamically active for Gyr time-scales on the WD's cooling track. On the other\nhand, systems with high-mass planets (100, 1000 $\\mathrm{M_\\oplus}$) lose up to\nfive planets, preferably by ejections, and become unstable in the first few\nhundred Myr after the formation of the WD.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Feb 2022 03:08:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-02"}
